name: Rabbit Hole with Jay and Rory
bio: A weekly standup show hosted by two Los Angeles and NerdMelt favorites, Jay Larson and Rory Scovel. Between Jay and Rory's playful banter, our eclectic mix of comedians, andÂ the trippy theme music from house band Drennon Davis, there's never a dull moment at Rabbit Hole!
copy: A new staple in the LA comedy scene, Rabbit Hole with Jay and Rory features an eclectic mix of comedians from national headliners to hilarious up-and-comers, all while keeping things wonderfully weird. Join us as we venture down the Rabbit Hole!
